lead_paragraph: Henrik Zetterberg scored in the eighth round of a shootout to give the Detroit Red Wings a 2-1 victory over the St. Louis Blues on Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: Detroit Defeats St. Louis After Marathon Shootout
